@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "ClassMate" {
    [Ui]
    [Parser]
    [CommandManager]
    [Storage]
    [ModulesLoader]

    rectangle "Model" {
        [UserProfile]
        [Major]
        [Module]
        [SpecialisationOverview]
        [Specialisation]
    }
}

User --> Ui : enters commands
Ui --> Parser : passes raw input
Parser --> CommandManager : creates command
CommandManager --> Model : reads / updates data
CommandManager --> Storage : saves / loads data
CommandManager --> Ui : returns result

ModulesLoader --> Model : loads module data at startup
Storage --> Model : persists user data

Ui ..> Parser : <<uses>>
Parser ..> CommandManager : <<uses>>
CommandManager ..> Model : <<uses>>
CommandManager ..> Storage : <<uses>>
ModulesLoader ..> Model : <<uses>>
Storage ..> Model : <<uses>>

@enduml
